channel.title: No one can get on my server
channel.description: Everytime I start my server no one can get on besides me. I portforwarded, and made sure the compile and run server things work. Everytime I start the server it says "Starting server on 0.0.0.0:43594" Is this normal? If it's not is there anyway I can fix it?

item.dc:creator: @Helbound Helbound
item.description:
@Helbound wrote:

[quote=“haticks, post:13, topic:141546”][quote author=Helbound link=topic=193835.msg1741926#msg1741926 date=1189313773]
Why cant I get on the RS2 Server Development/Help thing. I cant get to the posts, but the board isnt working… it just comes up a blank screen… the only reason I got to this thread is because I saw it saying ‘last post- wolflol’ next to the board link, and I click it, and I end up here. No matter what I do, I cant seem to the board… HELP!!!
[/quote]its down[/quote]
lol, kk. Its working now.
BTW, wolf, go now www.mine.nu, click the link to the Dynamic DNS thing. Then make a IP thing on there. On no-ip, you have to put in your own IP, but on Dynamic DNS, it puts it in for you, insuring that the new short Ip (ex- serverIP.servegame.com) will directly link to you. If you need any more help, pm me.
